The '''Supreme Administrative Court''' ({{lang-pt|Supremo Tribunal Administrativo}}) is a court in [[Portugal]] that deals with matters pertaining to administrative and fiscal legal relations. This court functions without prejudice to the jurisdiction of the [[Constitutional Court of Portugal]].
